sequenceDiagram
    participant Betradar as Betradar系统
    participant Client as 客户端系统
    participant DB as 本地数据库

    Note over Betradar,DB: 进球发生

    Betradar->>Client: odds_change(status=-1)<br/>进球确认前暂停
    Client->>DB: 更新Market状态为Suspended
    Client->>Client: 灰显相关Market
    Note over Client: 投注暂停

    Betradar->>Client: odds_change(status=1)<br/>进球确认
    Client->>DB: 更新Market状态为Active
    Client->>Client: 恢复Market显示
    Note over Client: 投注恢复

    Betradar->>Client: odds_change(status=0)<br/>某些Market停用<br/>赔率不再平衡
    Client->>DB: 更新Market状态为Deactivated
    Client->>Client: 灰显停用的Market
    Note over Client: 新赔率线条<br/>不再提供

    Betradar->>Client: odds_change(status=1)<br/>新赔率线条<br/>重新平衡
    Client->>DB: 更新新Market为Active
    Client->>Client: 显示新Market线条
    Note over Client: 新投注线条<br/>可用
